 type inequalities. For cases (2) and (3), the embeddings are characterized\nby the iso-capacitary inequality for fractonal Besov capacity of open sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jan 2022 17:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 15:34:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
