vity observations of H13CO+ and\nHC18O+ would be able to allow us to better constrain the oxygen fractionation\nin the disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 01:54:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
