e. The sizes of $\\nu$-clusters may range\nfrom $\\sim$ km to $\\sim 5$ Mpc. Formation of clusters affects perspectives of\ndetection of relic neutrinos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 02:20:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 13:34:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 15:04:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
