esults, we further\ninvestigate the influence of SR on infrared small target detection and the\nexperimental results demonstrate that MoCoPnet promotes the detection\nperformance. The code is available at https://github.com/XinyiYing/MoCoPnet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 07:20:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Jan 2022 03:07:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Jan 2022 16:08:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2022 14:33:58 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2023 14:25:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
