l way to reduce erosion symptoms; and (2) analyzing the trend of\nerosion symptoms can help get an insight about the erosion status of software\nsystems, and subsequently avoid the potential risk of architecture erosion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jan 2022 15:14:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
